          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>ID Badge Accessories Buying Guide for Schools</strong>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "caption_j8ndmz": {
          "type": "caption",
          "settings": {
            "caption": "Welcome!",
            "text_style": "caption-with-letter-spacing",
            "text_size": "medium"
          }
        },
        "text_9nTUEN": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Whether you're handling this for the first time or you've inherited this delightful task from someone who escaped to a different job, ordering ID badge accessories probably ranks pretty low on your daily excitement scale.</p><p>We get it. You're trying to get a bunch of students through the school year with their IDs intact, and frankly, that's already asking a lot.</p><p>That's why we wrote this guide - to make the whole process less painful and help you make a decision that won't come back to haunt you in the middle of the school year when someone asks, \"Who ordered these?\"</p><p><strong>Our goal?</strong> Be the easiest part of your procurement process.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
